According to http://www.mozilla.org/rhino/download.html

The source code for Rhino is available under MPL 1.1/GPL 2.0 license. In addition to getting the source from the zip files above, the source code for Rhino can be found in the CVS tree at mozilla/js/rhino. See source code via cvs for details on how to set up CVS, define your CVSROOT, and login. Once you've done that, just execute the command
